  (text "Each driver board:\n  1x PCA9685 TSSOP-28 (I2C PWM)\n  16x AO3400A SOT-23 (N-MOSFET)\n  16x 220Ω 0402 (gate resistor)\n  16x 1N4148WS SOD-323 (flyback diode)\n  16x 100nF 0402 (drain bypass)\n  1x 100µF electrolytic (VCC bulk)\n  1x JST-XH 4pin (I2C+5V in)\n  16x JST-SH 2pin (motor out)" (at 120 295 0)
